OL,3,CNottingham victims' families offered
OL,4,Cfree legal help by postmasters' lawyers
OL,6,FLawyers representing the Post Office
OL,7,Fsub-postmasters are to help the
OL,8,Ffamilies of the Nottingham attacks
OL,9,Fvictims in their fight for justice.
OL,11,FThey have offered their services pro
OL,12,Fbono to the relatives of Barnaby
OL,13,FWebber, Grace O'Malley-Kumar and Ian
OL,14,FCoates.
