OL,3,CNottingham victims' families offered
OL,4,Cfree legal help by postmasters' lawyers
OL,6,FThey will formally begin work on
OL,7,FFriday 14 June, a day after the city
OL,8,Fstopped to remember those killed and
OL,9,Finjured in the attacks on the first
OL,10,Fanniversary of the attacks.
OL,12,FMr Moloney has been representing
OL,13,Fvictims of the Post Office sub-
OL,14,Fpostmaster scandal in the ongoing
OL,15,FHorizon inquiry.
OL,17,FFormer Post Office chief executive
OL,18,FPaula Vennells was reduced to tears
OL,19,Fwhen she was grilled by the respected
OL,20,Fbarrister.
