OL,4,Cfree legal help by postmasters' lawyers
OL,6,FThe victims' families are calling for
OL,7,Fa change in the law to make it harder
OL,8,Ffor mentally ill killers to avoid
OL,9,Fmurder convictions.
OL,11,FValdo Calocane, 32, fatally stabbed 19-
OL,12,Fyear-old University of Nottingham
OL,13,Fstudents Mr Webber and Ms O'Malley-
OL,14,FKumar as they walked home in the early
OL,15,Fhours of June 13 last year, before
OL,16,Fkilling 65-year-old Mr Coates and
OL,17,Fstealing his van.
