OL,6,FHe then used the vehicle to knock down
OL,7,Fthree pedestrians ` Wayne Birkett,
OL,8,FMarcin Gawronski and Sharon Miller `
OL,9,Fin Nottingham city centre, before
OL,10,Fbeing arrested.
OL,12,FProsecutors accepted his not guilty
OL,13,Fpleas to murder at his sentencing at
OL,14,FNottingham Crown Court in January.
OL,16,FCalocane was given an indefinite
OL,17,Fhospital order after admitting
OL,18,Fmanslaughter by diminished
OL,19,Fresponsibility, after the court heard
OL,20,Fhe had been diagnosed with paranoid
OL,21,Fschizophrenia.
