OL,4,Cfree legal help by postmasters' lawyers
OL,6,FThe families are also calling for a
OL,7,Fpublic inquiry into the series of
OL,8,Ffailings that left him free to roam
OL,9,Fthe streets.
OL,11,FAuthorities missed a series of
OL,12,Fopportunities to detain Calocane, who
OL,13,Fwas on the run from Nottinghamshire
OL,14,FPolice for nine months before the
OL,15,Fkillings.
OL,17,FHe had been sectioned four times in
OL,18,Fthe previous three years but released
OL,19,Fback into the community on each
OL,20,Foccasion.
